23 13. A person who has acted in good faith to comply with state
24 reporting requirements and this section of law shall be immune from
Req. No. 16219 Page 17

1 liab ility for reporting allegations of abuse, neglect or
2 exploitation.
3 F. Each nurse aide trainee shall wear a badge which clearly
4 identifies the person as a nurse aide trainee. Such badge shall be
5 furnished by the facility employing the trainee. The badge shall be
6 nontransferable and shall include the first and last name of the
